1.0.name: wordpress/bikaner
1.0.description: Bikaner is fully responsive, clean, minimalist and mobile friendly theme. It is built with Twitter Bootstrap, mobile-first front-end framework. This is fully responsive and it's design changes according to mobile devices and the desktop or any other viewing environment. Theme features 5 Widget Areas, 2 Template Layouts, and it is Cross-Browser compatible. The theme features 4 footer widgets and top navigation bar with embedded search.
